# Railway Deployment Configuration
# 
# This app is ready to deploy on Railway with the following environment variables:
#
# Required:
#   - SYNC_TOKEN: Secret token for API authentication
#
# Optional:
#   - PORT: Server port (default: 8080)
#   - NODE_ENV: Environment (default: production)
#
# Deployment Instructions:
#
# 1. Via Web Dashboard:
#    - Visit: https://railway.app
#    - Connect your GitHub repository (zedanazad43/stp)
#    - Railway auto-detects Node.js and deploys
#
# 2. Via Railway CLI:
#    - npm install -g @railway/cli
#    - railway login
#    - railway up
#
# After deployment:
#    - API will be available at: https://<your-railway-domain>.railway.app
#    - Website: https://zedanazad43.github.io/stp/

